487
00:22:35,760 --> 00:22:37,800
That was the most expensive reunion I’ve ever been to.

488
00:22:37,880 --> 00:22:40,240
Well, at least you learned something about coordinating babysitters.

489
00:22:40,840 --> 00:22:42,760
Tell me, did you find the keys in the mess?

490
00:22:43,520 --> 00:22:46,040
Why?
-No, because you smell crazy like a mess.

491
00:22:46,120 --> 00:22:48,440
No, the keys were in a bag,
I was next to it so I tasted it.

492
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:50,320
What, you didn’t save me a piece?

493
00:22:51,320 --> 00:22:53,200
There were seven triangles,
I didn’t want to separate them.

494
00:22:53,680 --> 00:22:55,840
Try to put the girls to sleep in the living room,
they’ll fall asleep later,

495
00:22:55,920 --> 00:22:57,600
I’ll move them to the kitchen.
-Okay.

496
00:22:57,680 --> 00:22:58,960
Not the kitchen, the bedroom.
-No problem.

497
00:23:00,800 --> 00:23:03,120
You feel like he’s really joking.

498
00:23:07,560 --> 00:23:08,440
Hold on.

499
00:23:10,240 --> 00:23:12,480
I know the lines, I just...

500
00:23:13,360 --> 00:23:15,560
Took her to some movie, something.

501
00:23:16,400 --> 00:23:18,360
Again, a restaurant, why a movie?

502
00:23:18,440 --> 00:23:19,560
I found your bags.

503
00:23:24,760 --> 00:23:26,760
Meanwhile, seven crop-dusting planes
are taking off from the control tower.

504
00:23:27,080 --> 00:23:29,400
They’ll take off from Ovda Airport in the Negev, right?

505
00:23:29,480 --> 00:23:31,200
The control tower has a hard time taking off.

506
00:23:33,400 --> 00:23:36,360
It’s a madhouse. This won’t work like this.
-It’ll be fine, it’ll be fine, Meirav...

507
00:23:36,920 --> 00:23:37,880
Meirav...

508
00:23:37,960 --> 00:23:41,120
Why aren’t you looking for the keys?
-Mom...

